snippet.title: If you want to LAUGH, YOU NEED A PET! - Best funny ANIMAL compilation
snippet.description:
I'm sure you won't survive this laugh challenge, these animals are just TOO FUNNY! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, horses, monkeys, goats,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things, feel guilty... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
